```

## Breaking Changes

**None**. All new features are opt-in via configuration or UI controls.

## Performance Impact

**Topography**: Adds ~10 µs per agent per tick (terrain sampling + gradient calculation). Negligible for <10k agents.

**Selection**: Picking happens on mouse events (not every frame). O(n) scan of agent positions, but capped at ~100 µs for 10k agents (dominated by lock acquisition).

**Simulation pump**: Overhead <1% (timestep accumulator math is trivial).

